19 CONVICTED FELONS AND DELINQUENTS
19
20 A. Except as provided in subsection subsections B and C of this
20
21 section, it shall be unlawful for any person convicted of any felony
21
22 in any court of this state or of another state or of the United
22
23 States to have in his or her possession or under his or her
23
24 immediate control, or in any vehicle which the person is operating,
