11 1. “Sawed-off shotgun” or “sawed-off rifle” shall mean means
11
12 any shotgun or rifle of which the barrel or barrels have been
12
13 illegally shortened in length.
13
14 I. For purposes of this section, “altered toy pistol” shall
14
15 mean;
